1 guid elines as established by the Department and the Oklahoma State
2 Fire Marshal. No agency, municipality, county, or other political
3 subdivision of this state shall place stricter fire and life safety
4 requirements than those outlined in the 2018 International
5 Residential Code as adopted by the OUBCC on family child care homes
6 and large child care homes.
7 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
